source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Conservation Elements: Aquatic Intactness (HUC5)
source.description: This map provides an estimate of current and near-term aquatic intactness, which is based on the results of a fuzzy logic model integrating land use, water quality, hydrologic impacts, and road impacts.  It also shows long-term potential for climate change.
